fi.hiit.util

Class MetadataObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • fi.hiit.util.MetadataObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Experiment, Result, Subject, Task, TaskGroup

    public abstract class MetadataObject
extends java.lang.Object
    MetadataObject Represents an object which has metadata associtated with it.

    Metadata is held in a DataBundle object.

    Two metadata items are given special treatment, id and name.

    Both of these are arbitrary Strings and both are opitonal.

    Author:
    Konrad Markus
